  "key": "C major",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 3,
  "lyrics": "And the unity, they won't be mine As I see the sun come up over that mountain way I contemplate the way that I can't hide the rest of the trail Up the valleys and past the rock And the side roads of your favorite block All the way west, on your tracks and on your maps And I find myself, on my way to you With you, yeah, I'm on my way, baby On my way to you Now we take a little trip down the road Me and my big ol' truck and you and your Santa's hair blowin' wind Right in front of me is the golden Beautiful by me, can't think I'll ever see Play the eagles now, play the radio With your favorite song, keepin' along with it all In that time prime, countin' years, click visions In the back of the bus, singin' all the songs we lost, baby Time gets better when you lock it down and just stop Look around and hear the sound Community, laughin', hands clappin' And you're back to the start It's a sunrise up there, pop that now I'm lookin' for the ways up to your spot Do all your tracks and all of the crutches Findin' my way up right to where you are, baby Yeah, findin' my way up right to where you are Oh, baby, yeah Oh, right where you are",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 10.920000076293945,
      "text": "And the unity, they won't be mine",
      "start": 4.840000152587891
    },
    {
      "end": 17.139999389648438,
      "text": "As I see the sun come up over that mountain way",
      "start": 11.899999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 22.81999969482422,
      "text": "I contemplate the way that I can't hide the rest of the trail",
      "start": 17.139999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 28.700000762939453,
      "text": "Up the valleys and past the rock",
      "start": 23.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 34.2400016784668,
      "text": "And the side roads of your favorite block",
      "start": 29.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 39.84000015258789,
      "text": "All the way west, on your tracks and on your maps",
      "start": 35.20000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 46.20000076293945,
      "text": "And I find myself, on my way to you",
      "start": 39.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 51.20000076293945,
      "text": "With you, yeah, I'm on my way, baby",
      "start": 46.20000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 56.79999923706055,
      "text": "On my way to you",
      "start": 52.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 62.36000061035156,
      "text": "Now we take a little trip down the road",
      "start": 57.720001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 67.41999816894531,
      "text": "Me and my big ol' truck and you and your",
      "start": 62.720001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 69.66000366210938,
      "text": "Santa's hair blowin' wind",
      "start": 67.5
    },
    {
      "end": 73.58000183105469,
      "text": "Right in front of me is the golden",
      "start": 70.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 79.77999877929688,
      "text": "Beautiful by me, can't think I'll ever see",
      "start": 74.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 85.9000015258789,
      "text": "Play the eagles now, play the radio",
      "start": 80.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 92.36000061035156,
      "text": "With your favorite song, keepin' along with it all",
      "start": 86.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 97.31999969482422,
      "text": "In that time prime, countin' years, click visions",
      "start": 92.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 102.33999633789062,
      "text": "In the back of the bus, singin' all the songs we lost, baby",
      "start": 97.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 109.62000274658203,
      "text": "Time gets better when you lock it down and just stop",
      "start": 102.33999633789062
    },
    {
